trans-unit.source: Provides an interface to allow a composite-control designer to recreate the child controls of its associated control at design time.

A class derived from <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompositeControl> implements the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor> interface to allow its associated designer to call the control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor.RecreateChildControls%2A> method at design time.
trans-unit.target: 클래스에서 파생 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompositeControl> 구현 하는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor> 해당 연결 된 디자이너는 컨트롤을 호출할 수 있도록 인터페이스를 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor.RecreateChildControls%2A> 디자인 타임에 메서드.

trans-unit.source: The associated designer must derive from <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CompositeControlDesigner>.
The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor> interface is used primarily by control developers.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor> 인터페이스 주로 컨트롤 개발자가 사용 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: In a control derived from <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompositeControl" />, recreates the child controls at design time.
Called by the control's associated designer.

The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor.RecreateChildControls%2A> method allows a designer for a composite control to recreate the control's child controls at design time.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor.RecreateChildControls%2A> 메서드를 통해 복합 컨트롤에 대 한 디자이너 디자인 타임에 컨트롤의 자식 컨트롤을 다시 만들 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor.RecreateChildControls%2A> method is used primarily by control developers.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor.RecreateChildControls%2A> 주로 컨트롤 개발자가 메서드를 사용 합니다.
